"title": "4116: angels, opposed to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4116: angels, opposed to god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Spiritual beings who fell with Satan. They are under God's judgment and are subject to the authority of believers.</p>\n<h2>Spiritual authorities led by Satan</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:14\">2CO 11:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:11\">JHN 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:11\">REV 9:11</a></p>\n<h2>Angels opposed to God will be judged</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6\">JUD 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:18\">JOB 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:15\">JOB 15:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:4\">2PE 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ has defeated Satan and his angels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:15\">COL 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:21\">EPH 1:19–1:21</a></p>\n<h2>Satan's angels are resisted by God's faithful angels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:7-Rev12:9\">REV 12:7–12:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:13\">DAN 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:20\">DAN 10:20</a> <em>The princes of Persia and Greece appear to be spiritual powers who resist God's rule over these regions.</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ gives authority over Satan and his angels to believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:18-Luke10:19\">LUK 10:18–10:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:20\">ROM 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:3\">1CO 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10-Eph6:13\">EPH 6:10–6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">JAS 4:7</a></p>",
